{"results":[{"aya":"127","id":3915,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"他们否认他，所以他们必定要被拘禁。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"128","id":3916,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"惟真主的纯洁的众仆则不然。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"129","id":3917,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"我使他的令名，永存于后代。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"130","id":3918,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"祝易勒雅斯平安！","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"131","id":3919,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"我必定要这样报酬行善者。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"132","id":3920,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"他确是我的信道的仆人。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"133","id":3921,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"鲁特确是使者。","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":26,"previousPage":"/zh/s037-18.json","nextPage":"/zh/s037-20.json"}}